  yield tasks ≡ [
    "T3.1: Integrate Stripe for payment processing (API keys, webhook handlers, PCI compliance)",
    "T3.2: Implement subscription plans (free tier, basic, pro; plan selection, upgrades/downgrades)",
    "T3.3: Build free trial flow (14-day trial, trial-to-paid conversion, grace period handling)"
  ]
  yield rationale ≡ "3 tasks: payment pipe → plans → trial. T3.1 first (Stripe must work before plans), T3.2 and T3.3 sequential (trial depends on plans)."

  ⊨ 3 ≤ length(tasks) ≤ 5 → ✓ (3)

-- --- frame 7: task-decomposer-4 (SG4: go-to-market) ---

