--   normalization. But it's a concrete checkable step.
--
-- No truly vague actions found. All pass the "could a competent person
-- do this without asking 'but how?'" test.

  yield valid ≡ true
  yield vague-actions ≡ []
  yield total-actions ≡ 170

-- oracle checks:
--   ⊨ valid ∈ { true, false } → ✓ (true)
--   ⊨ vague-actions lists non-atomic actions → ✓ (empty — all atomic)
