  ∴ Assemble the full fractal plan...

  yield plan-tree ≡ "
GOAL: Launch SaaS invoicing product (3 months, 244 hours)
├── SG1: Core invoicing application (76h)
│   ├── T1.1: Data models + schema (16h, 4 steps, 10 actions)
