  yield summary ≡ "Fractal decomposition complete. 4 levels: 1 goal → 4 sub-goals → 15 tasks → 57 steps → 170 atomic actions. Total estimated: 244 hours across 3 months. All 4 validation oracles passed (no ⊥, no retries needed). Cross-cutting dependencies identified: T4.2 requires T1.2+T3.2, T1.2 requires T3.1 for payment status. 76 cells spawned (4 task-decomposers + 15 step-decomposers + 57 action-decomposers). Every leaf action is < 4 hours with a verifiable definition of done."

